{"tid":1153720,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[珍惜蘇蛇]靴里拉臨別撐蘇B：曼聯搵啱人","createTime":"2019-05-13T22:55:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-14T15:30:57.000Z","uid":31626,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"6f0b992bae6ed19c55046c2e735e6193a4b916e5","tid":1153720,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T22:55:11.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】與曼聯約滿離隊的安達靴里拉，力撐領隊蘇斯克查，認為曼聯委任他，是深慶得人。<br />\n<br />\n安達靴里拉（Ander Herrera）直言蘇斯克查面前有一份艱巨的工作，但強調挪威人是接受這份差事「適合的一個」，亦信任其教練團隊：「我實在對Ole（蘇斯克查）有信心，我實在相信米高（卡域克）、基蘭（麥堅拿）、米克費蘭及丹普斯（馬克丹普斯），但我認為面前是艱難的工作。」<br />\n<br />\n「這是我作為球迷，及某位了解球會目前狀況的人之意見。」該西班牙中場續說：「這些球迷是最好的，他們令人驚訝，但需要時間。球會需要時間、信心與支持。」<br />\n<br />\n靴里拉說：「但適當的人選正掌舵，他是合適的人選。」"},{"pid":"09e4deccb41f116d6ebe86b5b997d184bbb199f3","tid":1153720,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T23:23:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41a0cd4e188508382065192df2cc9ec1a0cda958","tid":1153720,"uid":103230,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T23:24:44.000Z","msg":"臨走都跣獌狗一腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a116effa0c0cb11ced4635c5b310816246a02ed","tid":1153720,"uid":19126,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T23:59:21.000Z","msg":"即係雲狗爾、摩狗閪之前係搵錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e156950b0381a7ceea6d5ff6c4490dc8e1126af","tid":1153720,"uid":29784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-14T00:19:26.000Z","msg":"戀愛大過天"},{"pid":"a2391731e486cdee9863d47fe03045c46a0b5af1","tid":1153720,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"41a0cd4e188508382065192df2cc9ec1a0cda958","tid":1153720,"uid":103230,"like":26,"dislike":4,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-13T23:24:44.000Z","msg":"臨走都跣獌狗一腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" c